summary:
I'm a Chilean graphic designer based in The Netherlands. I have an entrepreneur spirit and I'm passionate about understanding human behavior in order to bring solutions to social problems.
I have a vast experience working in international teams, which I really enjoy. 
Currently I am working in building a UX career.
